OL,3,CWill backlog of 20,000 tax returns
OL,4,Champer goods tax introduction?
OL,6,FTo say that Guernsey's Revenue Service
OL,7,Fhas been struggling is putting it
OL,8,Fmildly. Over the past several years,
OL,9,Fit has essentially collapsed.
OL,11,FIn fact, the situation is so serious
OL,12,Fthat the island's Treasury Lead said
OL,13,Fthat if the department were a school,
OL,14,Fit would be placed in 'Special
OL,15,FMeasures'.
OL,17,FThe scale now is undeniable: the
OL,18,FStates body responsible for collecting
OL,19,Ftaxes and paying rebates has a backlog
OL,20,Fof 20,000 tax returns.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
