OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1782402488
OL,3,CWill backlog of 20,000 tax returns
OL,4,Champer goods tax introduction?
OL,6,FFailed IT projects, backlogs, and the
OL,7,Ffallout of the pandemic have left the
OL,8,Fservice in tatters, and many members
OL,9,Fof the public have been waiting years
OL,10,Ffor rebates and returns.
OL,12,FThis fairly raises the question: If a
OL,13,FGoods and Services Tax is to be
OL,14,Fintroduced, how will the Revenue
OL,15,FService handle the extra work?
OL,17,FWe've been told that the Committee for
OL,18,FPolicy and Resources (P&R) finally has
OL,19,Fa full picture of the problem.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1782402488
OL,3,CWill backlog of 20,000 tax returns
OL,4,Champer goods tax introduction?
OL,6,FIn a statement today, the President of
OL,7,FP&R, Lindsay de Sausamarez, said:
OL,8,F"Since March, over 13,000 work items
OL,9,Fhave been processed, including the
OL,10,Fclearance of approximately 3,000
OL,11,Foutstanding repayments identified at
OL,12,Fthe end of February.
OL,14,F"The backlog of older personal tax
OL,15,Fcases has reduced by around 30%, debt
OL,16,Frecovery activity has restarted in a
OL,17,Fstructured manner, bereavement cases
OL,18,Fhave been fully triaged, and more than
OL,19,F5,000 customers have already benefited
OL,20,Ffrom recovery actions.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1782402488
OL,3,CWill backlog of 20,000 tax returns
OL,4,Champer goods tax introduction?
OL,6,F"Assessments for 2024 will be released
OL,7,Fin a controlled and phased way to
OL,8,Fensure that any resulting repayments
OL,9,Fcan be processed promptly and customer
OL,10,Fdemand can be managed effectively."
OL,12,FThe hope and promise is that by the
OL,13,Fend of 2027, Revenue Services will be
OL,14,Fback on track.
OL,16,FHowever, not everyone shares this
OL,17,Fconfidence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@cO]
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1782402488
OL,3,CWill backlog of 20,000 tax returns
OL,4,Champer goods tax introduction?
OL,6,FDeputy Neil Inder said to get
OL,7,Fislanders back on side, public targets
OL,8,Fneed to be set to ensure absolute
OL,9,Ftransparency.
OL,11,FWhen asked if he trusts that the
OL,12,FRevenue Service will be ready for a
OL,13,Fpotential GST in 2028, he said: "I
OL,14,Fhave no confidence at all.
OL,16,F"When a 'school' is under 'Special
OL,17,FMeasures', you usually sack the
OL,18,Fleadership and put more funding into
OL,19,Fit, but what you don't do is put more
OL,20,Fchildren in.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1782402488
OL,3,CWill backlog of 20,000 tax returns
OL,4,Champer goods tax introduction?
OL,6,F"Adding more problems for Revenue
OL,7,FServices while in the middle of
OL,8,Falready existing ones doesn't seem
OL,9,Flike a good idea."
OL,11,FTo try and avoid this, P&R has begun a
OL,12,Frecovery plan, split into two phases:
OL,13,Fstabilising now, then longer-term
OL,14,Ftransformation.
OL,16,FWith any potential GST expected by
OL,17,F2028, the clock is ticking for the
OL,18,FRevenue Service to get its house in
OL,19,Forder.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/6
